            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card h-25 p-2" style="width: 18rem;">
            <img class="card-img-top rounded" src="https://eriksbikeshop.vtexassets.com/arquivos/ids/337785/2023FourstrokeLTLTDFullSuspensionMountainBike.jpg?v=638070654093270000">
